        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(feishu): pace outbound sends per target",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes #14206.\n\nFeishu outbound sends currently retry after the API returns rate-limit responses, but configured high-volume conversations can still burst several `im.message.create` / `im.message.reply` calls to the same Feishu target at once. That makes the first user-visible symptom a Feishu rate-limit error instead of a paced send queue.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nThis adds an opt-in `channels.feishu.sendRateLimit.minIntervalMs` setting, with the same setting available under `channels.feishu.accounts.<id>.sendRateLimit.minIntervalMs` for per-account overrides. When configured, Feishu text, card, image, and file message sends are paced by account + receive id type + receive id. Different Feishu targets still send independently, and the default interval remains `0` so existing installs keep their current behavior unless they opt in.\n\n## User Impact\n\nOperators can set a small per-target send interval to avoid Feishu per-chat send bursts while keeping cross-chat throughput. Existing retry handling for Feishu 230020 / 11232 / 429 responses remains in place for server-side limits that still occur.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run extensions/feishu/src/send.concurrent.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/config-schema.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/send.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/send-target.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/send.retry.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run extensions/feishu/src/outbound.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run extensions/feishu/src/reply-dispatcher.test.ts`\n- `oxfmt --check extensions/feishu/src/send-rate-limit.ts extensions/feishu/src/send-target.ts extensions/feishu/src/send.ts extensions/feishu/src/media.ts extensions/feishu/src/config-schema.ts extensions/feishu/src/config-schema.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/send.concurrent.test.ts extensions/feishu/openclaw.plugin.json`\n- `git diff --check`",
        "branch": "codex/feishu-send-rate-limit",
